reviewText: Love it! It is fun, informative, and awesomely humorous. The 3 disc set covers a wide range of foods from stew to ice cream. I think Good Eats is the most entertaining cooking show out there, hands down.
Bought this for my mom last Christmas. She's a huge fan. She loves this DVD and hopes to get more! Alton Brown is a wickedly talented guy who puts a very original spin on cooking shows!
